name: The Big Shot
description:
The Big Shot also know as "Jolly Paradise" is a unique whiskey and soda beverage with vodka infused with blue raspberry gummy bears at the rim coated with strawberry pucker powder.

The Big Shot is only collected by authentic collectors of the 'Candy Martini Bar Collection.' 

Collectors must collect 6/6 art pieces of the Candy Martini Bar Collection to get this NFT transferred to them at no cost.

Licensed Track: Детство REMIX • 🎧 [MusicOcean]
